aspguidp.service.data.manager.impl

Class SimpleValueDataManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • aspguidp.service.data.manager.impl.SimpleValueDataManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AtomConsumer, AtomSupplier, DataManager, ValueDataManager

    public class SimpleValueDataManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements ValueDataManager
    Basic implementation of the ValueDataManager interface which uses an EntityFactory instance to create Entity instances from given user input strings and string representations of atoms.
